{"tid":2500202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立陶宛：退出與中國的「17+1合作」　在台灣設立經貿辦事處","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:44:24.000Z","uid":261647,"like":121,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5e96f050871420e9cf4954d95ff3be04ed1b39b4","tid":2500202,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongyikmohk/posts/300499924927646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongyikmohk%2Fposts%2F300499924927646&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=d5db99e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongyikmohk/posts/300499924927646</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmedhSEPKxg2LDKmY6WZwYUcWgW9ajohF8CLWoFpFpG25M?filename=0mAx4Fu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mAx4Fu.png&h=0d2dcd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃奕武 WONG Yik Mo<br />\n<br />\n17+1是個中國與中、東歐國家間的非正式合作，17代表歐洲國家，包括巴爾幹的阿爾巴尼亞、波斯尼亞、波羅地海的立陶宛、愛沙尼亞、其他歐盟國家的保加利亞、捷克、希臘、匈牙利等等，而 ＋1則是中國。這個合作計劃表面上是促進經貿合作，但眾所周知，這是中國用來分化歐洲的手段。<br />\n<br />\n立陶宛外長今年年初，在國會同意退出17+1後，對媒體表示「17+1對立陶宛基本上沒有帶來任何利益... 這個合作對歐洲也沒有什麼好處，反而只會分化歐洲國家。」<br />\n<br />\n近年來，17+1內的歐盟國家均對中國感到不滿，像是一直承諾的投資，尤其是一帶一路，不增反減。最近歐中關係又因為香港、新疆集中營、新疆棉與互相制裁等等搞的一塌糊塗，以致不少國家都在考慮退出17+1。<br />\n<br />\n立陶宛外交部向媒體表示，17+1並不是正式的組織，故立陶宛不會正式退出，而是直接不再參與。另外，立陶宛打算在台灣開設經貿辦事處，一般理解為大使館，以促進經貿合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lrt.lt/en/news-in-english/19/1378043/we-will-not-be-intimidated-despite-china-threats-lithuania-moves-to-recognise-uighur-genocide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lrt.lt%2Fen%2Fnews-in-english%2F19%2F1378043%2Fwe-will-not-be-intimidated-despite-china-threats-lithuania-moves-to-recognise-uighur-genocide&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=178cdd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lrt.lt/en/news-in-english/19/1378043/we-will-not-be-intimidated-despite-china-threats-lithuania-moves-to-recognise-uighur-genocide</a>"},{"pid":"c3d9fffb6c7a9b742b399c04f5b677a03afa6390","tid":2500202,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"支國： 強烈反對 反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0db529a2fd7f600628ff19fb31188daadd91511","tid":2500202,"uid":54323,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"估下今次出唔出石頭<br />\n<br />\n正皮：出<br />\n負皮：唔出"},{"pid":"fcee0d030692256ed5da08c2c0427dfc86a1e407","tid":2500202,"uid":290118,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"東歐勇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n匈牙利真係垃圾"},{"pid":"7fbb196aba9d16408b7acd6cbd901c182b4f42aa","tid":2500202,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"小心支那發脾氣<br />\n製造另一隻病毒攬炒全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4078615a5b3623448ad21f940a11182a772b1d11","tid":2500202,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4511e1b9012c6112be9901db42938bfe67ca6346","tid":2500202,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"口交部：嬲 石頭 腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c0dfb0789db154d1dbf34423053d1aa9faf445","tid":2500202,"uid":34358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr